Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.19,0:00:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看見我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼傷心的事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…那個…你在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我很開心 因為我一直都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得無法跟大家相處得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你願意跟我在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:00:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會弄疼你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著？究竟是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是傳聞中的賽托希梅亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是教會的使者嗎 你們就放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是巴爾思庫拉的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有想去解除那傢伙的封印 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教會？那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 是那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是信仰魔神的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也死不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞 你給了他什麼力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 該死 該死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:03:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死 該死 為什麼救不了她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了六次還是殺不死他呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 他不是多少次都能復活的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說有次數限制呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 正確答案是他第七次就無法復活了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隱瞞什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個法術15分鐘就會重置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時開始 就能再死6次呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我對大兔下的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡上他了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓喜歡上的人不會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他不死 永遠陪伴在自己身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給予了他愚蠢的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會照你說的做的 不要再在大兔面前羞辱我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太麻煩了 我要消除他的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我不要忘記希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會去救希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定…一定不會把希梅亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向？ 不要把我和那個無聊的渣滓混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月光？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎 後背
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要對希梅亞動手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為日向在追那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:02.76,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(500,500)\be10\pos(238,122)}「放學後的900秒（後篇）」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 雜魚沒有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的還算快 但不是我的對手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是被上古魔法師施下了詛咒的可悲犧者的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買可樂回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…頭滾飛出去 然後卡吧的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了 不死身君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是敵人 美雷快點幹掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慘的樣子 我們反而比較像壞人喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 月光一直都是壞人就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 當壞人的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 聽我命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活力百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安度的米蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個安藤美雷嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶哩嗶哩上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一招也嗶哩嗶哩電麻你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了月光 我不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的雜魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形勢逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 先把劍扔下怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那麼做的話我可不能保證人質會變成什麼樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開美雷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 月光為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 拖後腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為對付他們這種雜魚不需要用劍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼去死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在心情超級好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就稍微拿出點真本事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要飛到哪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的彈跳力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還有別的地方應該誇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久別重逢時說這種話 可是不會受歡迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上就是不受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你受我歡迎 這就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你件好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:11:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會燙 那是連我們上古魔法師都無法使用的禁咒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用這火焰的瞬間 上半身就會被燒成飛灰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我這個人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 我的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那樣 用這個把他幹掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 現在投降的話還能饒你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶劍破邪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜魚別囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.15,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫月光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼全都去死如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:11:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜘蛛？！ 話說好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光有兩個？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是又來追我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這傢伙把希梅亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要插手 他由我來砍掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 渣滓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個明明是雙胞胎卻像屎一樣的殘次品弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的獵物！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 究竟殘次品是哪邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我用過的二手貨收為了棋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二手貨…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 美雷 你剛受到的侮辱我很快就會幫你還清
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怪物 交給你行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能行 幹死它喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 能行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是我可靠的拍檔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們跑吧 大兔 趁現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不贏那傢伙的 太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直等了我9年 能不能順便…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等5分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去揍那傢伙 然後回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我也一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太自戀 大兔一個人肯定贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但兩個人的話也許能行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔在這9年間也變得非常強大、帥氣了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全忘記了希梅亞的存在而平凡地生活到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有稍微努力過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾在空手道上有一定的成就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那一定是為了希梅亞而去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再次相見了 這次絕對要保護她！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶哩嗶哩電他去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你稍微有些進步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微努力了一下後 發現在不經意間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經領先了你2萬步左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2萬步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是指在我身後2萬步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為這種程度的力量就囂張呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃開笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進了2萬步還是拖後腿角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鐵大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於坦率一點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是被嘲笑了還能若無其事跑掉的沒骨氣傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼提案嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再發出那個一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那由你去幹掉他 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經束手無策了吧 那就結束好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下賽托希梅亞 其他人都殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者做個以你們3人的性命交換她的交易也行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊都拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你 保護希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的力量確實有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她給你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 明明拷問過你那麼多次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻沒有給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在最危險的是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第6次了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9年前的再現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真是沒進步呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 還是如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次請好好發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓成為我的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是奴隸還是什麼的我都當
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不要殺大兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為他的奴隸什麼的 這種事不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 這次我一定會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡等好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去揍那傢伙 然後回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來保護？在這狀況下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再死可就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命 等於是希梅亞給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拯救希梅亞的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她失去了的9年 如果今後希梅亞能笑著活下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這條命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 你辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.66,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到的 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再次把希梅亞忘記了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是雜魚 但做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…又把你弄哭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡迷糊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是轉學生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希…希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.77,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅月光？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起你就是我的奴隸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的學生會幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是奴隸呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是卑微的奴隸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說要我直接教給你的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:22:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意 昨天的勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說希梅亞 能不能放開我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後都會和大兔在一起了 好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不要擅自決定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無意聽命於你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所有故事的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的連接世界與世界的屎一樣麻煩故事的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然被殺掉又活過來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有絕世美少女說最喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被鳥火的學生會長把我當奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的高中生活究竟會變成什麼樣？！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.59,0:24:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看來是不會無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.80,0:24:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟希梅亞又可愛又軟又好聞…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.44,0:24:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 這樣我真能活過這三年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 已經死了一次了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.13,0:24:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不是那種問題吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.08,0:24:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(440,130)\1c&H0BFFFF&\3c&HD163ED&\bord2\3a&H3A&\shad1\4c&H8F8F8F&}下集「《月亮》搖曳的泳池邊」
